  description = 'Trains hamstring-glute strength, hip hinge control, and balance for landing, stride, and fielding transfer.',
  card_summary = 'Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift is a throwing-athlete exercise for trains hamstring-glute strength, hip hinge control, and balance for landing, stride, and fielding transfer.',
  coach_language = 'Coach Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift as throwing mobility, rib-scap access, and activation work. Use it when it supports the thrower''s kinetic chain without stealing quality from skill throwing, speed, or recovery.',
